fields.name: Profile Pic Description
fields.value: My cat Moxie peeking out of a tan carpeted cat tree window. Moxie is a tabby w/ green eyes, brown fur with black striped forehead "M", and a white stripe that covers her nose and up to between her eyes. Her left ear and face are obscured.

fields.name: Header Pic Description
fields.value: A 1960s washed-out pic of an old farm. The barn and some tall trees are in shadows in the background, with a mown grass field in front. From a distance in the foreground are 3 children, lined up tallest to shortest, with tallest on the left.
